"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The UAE has issued an emergency alert, telling people to find shelter. Earlier, the country stopped six Iranian missiles and 131 drones. The Iranian military's actions come as there are rumors that the US wants Iranian Kurdish groups to join its fight with Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"UAE Emergency Alert\",            \"translated_version\": \"El UAE ha dado una alerta de emergencia, diciendo a la gente que busque refugio. Antes, el pa\u00eds par\u00f3 seis misiles iran\u00edes y 131 drones. Las acciones del ej\u00e9rcito iran\u00ed vienen porque hay rumores de que Estados Unidos quiere que grupos kurdos iran\u00edes se unan a su pelea con Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Alerta de Emergencia en UAE\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Huge traffic jams happened after a warning for people to leave the Hezbollah area, as Israel increases its attacks across Lebanon.\",            \"english_title\": \"Traffic Jams in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"Grandes atascos de tr\u00e1fico pasaron despu\u00e9s de una advertencia para que la gente salga del \u00e1rea de Hezbollah, porque Israel aumenta sus ataques en todo L\u00edbano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Atascos en L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ecuador's military says they found a drug-trafficking submersible that was filled with fuel and ready to go.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ecuador Finds Submersible\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Ecuador dice que encontraron un submarino de tr\u00e1fico de drogas que estaba lleno de combustible y listo para ir.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ecuador Encuentra Submarino\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine's president says Kyiv will only help if it does not weaken its own air defenses.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine's Condition\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania dice que Kyiv solo ayudar\u00e1 si no debilita sus propias defensas a\u00e9reas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Condici\u00f3n de Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Canadian prime minister said Australia and Canada should work together as 'strategic cousins'.\",            \"english_title\": \"Canada and Australia Partnership\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de Canad\u00e1 dijo que Australia y Canad\u00e1 deben trabajar juntos como `primos estrat\u00e9gicos`.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Asociaci\u00f3n de Canad\u00e1 y Australia\"        }    ]}"